data.meta_description: August weather for Munka-Ljungby, Sweden: The month with the most rainfall in Munka-Ljungby, Sweden, is August, when the rain falls for 20.8 days and typically aggregates up to 73mm (2.87") of precipitation. The last month of the summer, August, is also an agreeable month in Munka-Ljungby, Sweden, with temperature in the range of an average low of 14.7°C (58.5°F) and an average high of 20.1°C (68.2°F).
